Source:   GeoNames <https://www.geonames.org>
Licence:  Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
          <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/>
Files:    assets/cities.tsv  (committed)
          assets/cities_precise.tsv  (generated locally, not in repo)
          assets/cities_detailed.tsv (generated locally, not in repo)
Script:   scripts/fetch_cities.py downloads the source data from
          <https://download.geonames.org/export/dump/cities1000.zip>

Modifications applied to GeoNames data:
  – Selected rows with population ≥ 1 000 (cities_detailed.tsv),
    ≥ 5 000 (cities_precise.tsv), or top 5 000 by population (cities.tsv).
  – Retained columns: name, country code, latitude, longitude, population,
    timezone.  All other GeoNames columns discarded.

